30 Trance Classics (2013) 

                             Trance | Essential Dance

            320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-11-04 | 04:03:42 | 560 Mb


Oh my, what a collection of classics we have for you the discerning trance fanatic! Our team have scratched their collective heads and whittled the hundreds of classic trancers down to just 30 and present to you 30 Trance Classics. Featuring the production talents of the cream of the trance crop this collection tips it hat to the hay day of trance evoking many a memory with uplifting tracks such as Onova Platitude, Vimana We Came and Cold Blue Paradise right through to the darn right banging Tiesto remix of Umeks Gatex and who could forget Mojados seminal tech trancer Naranja? There all here in one bumper collection, so theres no need to search out the individual classics were done all the hard work for you!
